01:27:44.920 --> 01:27:46.409
John Ellis: You can make tool calls.

427
01:27:47.430 --> 01:27:52.289
John Ellis: And we want to make sure that useful things get put into context.

428
01:27:54.690 --> 01:28:07.359
John Ellis: And it doesn't matter if you're talking about text, or if you're talking about images, all of those can be tokenized. All of those can be represented as embeddings, so it's multimodal, depending on whether you trained it on the multimodal to begin with.

429
01:28:08.700 --> 01:28:11.239
John Ellis: The key thing is… tools.

