01:32:36.340 --> 01:32:48.840
John Ellis: that should severely restrict how you think about what it's going to be doing. It's going to be doing a lot more plausible answers than actually approval. Nice thing about these kinds of, like, computer… if it writes computer code, now you have traceability.

