01:36:36.460 --> 01:36:38.969
John Ellis: This is where skills come in.

509
01:36:40.070 --> 01:36:51.320
John Ellis: We're going to be taking a much deeper look at skills in just a little bit, but know the following. Skills are a collection of human-authored, by and large, human-authored

