01:36:51.420 --> 01:36:54.940
John Ellis: documents On how to do things.

511
01:36:56.580 --> 01:36:58.070
John Ellis: And here's how you think about it.

512
01:36:58.900 --> 01:37:09.510
John Ellis: Skills, you can have a large collection of skills that tell you how to do a particular thing. Could be an analysis, could be a particular type of work, we're going to see lots of different examples of this.

513
01:37:09.740 --> 01:37:14.160
John Ellis: What the model does is… You ask it to do something.

514
01:37:14.330 --> 01:37:18.780
John Ellis: And the first thing it does is assess whether or not there exists a skill

