01:37:22.870 --> 01:37:37.040
John Ellis: which is the preferred way for you, your lab group, your organization, to solve a particular problem. It first looks to see if there's a standard, good way to do this. If it is, it takes up that one skill.

517
01:37:37.820 --> 01:37:39.410
John Ellis: And puts it into the prompt.

518
01:37:41.440 --> 01:37:44.950
John Ellis: But it only does so when you ask it to do that thing.

