534
01:39:00.340 --> 01:39:05.740
John Ellis: I consider this to be an extremely important socio-technical advancement.

535
01:39:06.310 --> 01:39:16.070
John Ellis: Because this does a couple of very important things. One, it gives us traceability. We're going to be talking just a little bit about human and AI interaction. It's important for that. It is human author

