584
01:44:46.450 --> 01:44:57.249
John Ellis: That, in terms of model performance, it is no longer the case that one model is just better than another. It's the combination of model and harness.

585
01:44:57.480 --> 01:45:07.339
John Ellis: That's what's being discussed now. Do you have a good agent harness that allows you to do these things and gives you the observability in order to do these tasks?

586
01:45:07.600 --> 01:45:19.300
John Ellis: When Matt was talking before about allowing the computer to work for about 8 hours, what he was talking about, he gave it a task, gave it information, and said, write this code, work on it until it works.

587
01:45:20.910 --> 01:45:22.130
